    </div>
</div>
              <div class="w3-bar-item field__item">    <div class="view-node-display-card-wrapper"  data-history-node-id="3132720" about="/blog/how-uk-financing-new-billions-climate-and-ukraine">
      <a href="/blog/how-uk-financing-new-billions-climate-and-ukraine">
        <div class="w3-bar-item field__item">
          <img src="https://www.cgdev.org/sites/default/files/2023-08/Uk_flag.jpeg"  alt="Flag of the United Kingdom "  loading="lazy" typeof="foaf:Image" class="w3-image image-style-card-cover">
        </div>
        <h6 class="view-card-title">Blog Post</h6>
                      
            <div class="field field--name-field-short-title field--type-string field--label-hidden w3-clear w3-bar-item field__item">How the UK is Financing New Billions for Climate and Ukraine</div>
      
                </a>
      <div class="w3-clear field field--name-field-authors field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__items">
                                          <div class="w3-bar-item field__item">    
      <a href="http://www.cgdev.org/expert/ian-mitchell">  Ian Mitchell
  
</a>
    

                              et al.
